Hiranandani Bhiwandi holds the elegance of a pristine residential development in Mumbai, Maharashtra. Boasted by its vibrant & verdant environment, this under-construction residential project has its exuberant spread over huge acres of land. The property has flamboyantly built towers and Apartments are available in the configurations of 2, 3 & 4 BHK apartments. Conceptualised, envisaged & developed from scratch by one of the well-known builders Hiranandani Group, the residences here are built with high-quality construction materials & entail no compromise on the residents' safety.
